  "hierarchicalProperty": "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf",
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000179": "t-region",
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000180": "TemporalRegion",
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116": {
    "axioms": [
      {
        "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/0000003",
        "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": "per discussion with Barry Smith"
      }
    ],
    "type": [
      "reification"
    ],
    "value": "Temporal region doesn't have a closure axiom because the subclasses don't exhaust all possibilites. An example would be the mereological sum of a temporal instant and a temporal interval that doesn't overlap the instant. In this case the resultant temporal region is neither 0-dimensional nor 1-dimensional"
  },
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000600": {
    "axioms": [
      {
        "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/100-001"
      }
    ],
    "type": [
      "reification"
    ],
    "value": "A temporal region is an occurrent entity that is part of time as defined relative to some reference frame. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [100-001])"
  },
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000601": [
    {
      "axioms": [
        {
          "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/101-001"
        }
      ],
      "type": [
        "reification"
      ],
      "value": "All parts of temporal regions are temporal regions. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [101-001])"
    },
    {
      "axioms": [
        {
          "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/119-002"
        }
      ],
      "type": [
        "reification"
      ],
      "value": "Every temporal region t is such that t occupies_temporal_region t. (axiom label in BFO2 Reference: [119-002])"
    }
  ],
  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000602": [
    {
      "axioms": [
        {
          "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/100-001"
        }
      ],
      "type": [
        "reification"
      ],
      "value": "(forall (x) (if (TemporalRegion x) (Occurrent x))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [100-001] "
    },
    {
      "axioms": [
        {
          "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/101-001"
        }
      ],
      "type": [
        "reification"
      ],
      "value": "(forall (x y) (if (and (TemporalRegion x) (occurrentPartOf y x)) (TemporalRegion y))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [101-001] "
    },
    {
      "axioms": [
        {
          "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0010000": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/bfo/axiom/119-002"
        }
      ],
      "type": [
        "reification"
      ],
      "value": "(forall (r) (if (TemporalRegion r) (occupiesTemporalRegion r r))) // axiom label in BFO2 CLIF: [119-002] "
    }
  ],
